;; Assail Classifications — proven
;; ===============================
;;
;; Records panic-attack assail findings audited and classified as legitimate.
;; See panic-attack/.claude/CLAUDE.md § "User-Classification Registry" for the
;; canonical format. The registry is a separate file from any source under
;; scan — adding a new unsafe block in production code cannot self-suppress,
;; the classification edit is always a reviewable companion change.

